longBusinessSummary: Empire Global Gaming, Inc. engages in gaming business worldwide. The company develops a line of public and casino grade gaming products for roulette, blackjack, craps, baccarat, mini baccarat, pinwheels, Sic Bo, slot machines, poker tables, and bingo games. It also offers consulting and advisory services to the gaming industry. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Bellport, New York.
